velocity all create 300 40450 rot yes dist gaussian

fix fxlang all langevin ${T_target} ${T_target} 1000.0 30552
fix fxlang all langevin 300 ${T_target} 1000.0 30552
fix fxlang all langevin 300 300 1000.0 30552
fix fxnve  all nve
fix recenter all momentum 1000 linear 1 1 1

